  "body": "This is a patch release mostly to fix an issue where the sessions in the session-manager would take ~1 minute to be updated.\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* Fix typo in help page by @wendrul in https://github.com/zellij-org/zellij/pull/2906\r\n* fix(sessions): untie serialization interval from session read interval by @imsnif in https://github.com/zellij-org/zellij/pull/2951\r\n* fixup: zellij-server: fix compiler warnings by @rmsyn in https://github.com/zellij-org/zellij/pull/2873\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @wendrul made their first contribution in https://github.com/zellij-org/zellij/pull/2906\r\n* @rmsyn made their first contribution in https://github.com/zellij-org/zellij/pull/2873\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/zellij-org/zellij/compare/v0.39.1...v0.39.2",
